q.1(check even and odd number)
num = int (input("Enter Number: "))
if (num % 2 )==0:
    print("The number is EVEN:")
else:
    print ("The number is ODD:")
Enter Number: 86
The number is EVEN
Enter Number: 49
The number is ODD

q.2(check number is +,-, or 0)
num = int(input("Enter a number: "))
if num > 0:
   print("Positive number")
elif num == 0:
   print("Zero")
else:
   print("Negative number")
Enter a number: 45
Positive number
Enter a number: -56
Negative number
Enter a number: 0
Zero

q.3(find largest number)
dic=[1,23,44,67,90,87,54,33]
print("Largest number of the list is:", max(dic))
Largest number of the list is: 90
